threads.title: 820-3437 sometimes no S5 from PCH
threads.message:
PP3V3_S5  always present
32khz for PCH always present
PM_PWRBTN_L always present
PM_RSMRST_L always present
PPVRTC_G3H always present
RTC_RESET_L always present
PM_SLP_S5_L sometimes present, sometimes miss when I reconect magsafe.

Any idea what could be wrong?

When PM_SLP_S5_L present no fan spinning.

threads.title: 820-3437 sometimes no S5 from PCH
threads.message:
When PM_SLP_S5_L is missing is PM_PCH_SYS_PWROK present out of U1950?
Known good DC in board and cable?

threads.title: 820-3437 sometimes no S5 from PCH
threads.message: Could be anything, inspect for corrosion. Was machine dropped?
